<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0de40106-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s4074"><num value="4074">§ 4074.</num><heading> Construction</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of this subchapter shall supersede all other provisions of Federal law that are inconsistent with the provisions of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0de40107-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/377/tVIII/s805">Pub. L. 98–377, title VIII, § 805</ref>, <date date="1984-08-11">Aug. 11, 1984</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/98/1304">98 Stat. 1304</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
